title: Looking for 5 vs 5 ranked team
body:
Feel free to add me on 'hashshashin' currently mid silver looking for any ranked team really, willing to play a few normals or ranked duo before joining to see if i will fit with the team. I have been playing for a while so i'm fine with most roles though would prefer not to go with support though if needed might consider it.

On a side note also willing to duo with probably anyone of any rank as long as you don't go negative every game.

replies.body:
Hey pal,

I'm also looking for people to play ranked with. I'm Silver 5 and have played ~30 ranked matches, 320 normal wins - I'm not great. Just looking to play with similar leveled people who don't rage/quit/afk etc.

Cheers.
